title: Three by Three Jotblock Portable Studio Essentials
description:
Get carried away! The new Portable Studio Essentials set invites experimentation. Felt carrying case opens to reveal a wood tray with a variety of neatly arranged, easily accessible supplies in individualized compartments. Heavy-duty magnet snaps close the case securely for safe travels. 

  • Dimensions: 12.5 x 8.25 x 1.5 in.
  • Materials: 100% recycled felt case. Wood supply tray. Pencils, markers, and tools for drawing & sketching. Watercolor pencils and brushes for painting. 2-sided combo pad with sketching paper & watercolor paper.
